        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-300 mb-2">Social Media Marketing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Boost your online presence and engage your audience with expert multi-platform strategies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Service Card 5: Website Optimization -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-black to-gray-900 border border-blue-900/50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl cursor-pointer service-card" data-tooltip="Improve loading speeds, SEO, and user experience.">
        <div class="mb-4 text-blue-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="m16.2 7.8 2.9-2.9"/><path d="M18 12h4"/><path d="m16.2 16.2 2.9 2.9"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="m4.9 19.1 2.9-2.9"/><path d="M2 12h4"/><path d="m4.9 4.9 2.9 2.9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-300 mb-2">Website Optimization</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Enhance performance and search rankings with technical SEO and speed improvements.
